title: Rep. Matt Gaetz triggers vote to oust Kevin McCarthy from speaker's office
description: Rep. Matt Gaetz filed a motion to force a vote to oust Kevin McCarthy as speaker of the House.

title: Girl who disappeared in New York state park is found alive,  police say
description: The 9-year-old girl who authorities suspected was abducted Saturday in an upstate New York state park was found alive, state police said Monday night.

title: Woman alleges Disney waterslide caused dangerous 'wedgie' that left her with severe injuries
description: A woman says she was severely injured on a waterslide at a Disney park during her 30th birthday celebration.

title: 'Sunday Night Football' scores ratings TD as Swifites tune in with Jets, Chiefs fans
description: An average of 27 million people tuned into the Chiefs- Jets game — which Taylor Swift also attended — making it the most-watched Sunday TV show since the Super Bowl, according to NBC Sports.

title: Why Gen. Mark Milley stressed repeatedly that the military had 'zero role' in electoral politics
description: The former chairman of the joint chiefs of staff Gen. Mark Milley tells NBC News’ Lester Holt that it’s vital for the American military to stay out of politics.

title: North Dakota lawmaker and his family killed in Utah plane crash
description: BISMARCK, N.D. — A state senator from North Dakota, his wife and their two young children died when the small plane they were traveling in crashed in Utah, a Senate leader said Monday.

title: Coast Guard calls off search for man reported missing after possible shark attack in California
description: The U.S. Coast Guard has called off a search for a man who was reportedly attacked by a shark Sunday morning in northern California, officials said.

title: Jodie Turner-Smith files for divorce from Joshua Jackson
description: Jodie Turner-Smith has filed for divorce from Joshua Jackson, according to a petition she filed in Los Angeles.

title: Video shows bloodied Black man surrounded by officers during Florida traffic stop
description: A traffic stop captured on video by a bystander shows a handcuffed Black man with swollen eyes and a bloody face sitting on the ground surrounded by officers outside a vehicle in northeast Florida, and the officers’ law enforcement agency says it has launched an internal review.

title: Oklahoma mom killed after being hit by the wing of small plane while on lawn mower
description: An Oklahoma woman has died after she was hit by a small plane at a small airport in Broken Bow, Oklahoma, on Friday afternoon.

title: Sophie Turner submits letter Joe Jonas wrote about making 'a permanent home' in England, court docs show
description: Sophie Turner has filed legal documents that include a letter she says was written by estranged husband Joe Jonas about looking for "a permanent home" for their children in England before their split.

title: Jan. 6 rioter who urged mob to take officer's guns took a secret plea deal, DOJ confirms
description: Jan. 6 defendant Samuel Lazar took a secret plea deal and was sentenced to 2.5 years in prison earlier this year, the Justice Department said n a new filing.

title: 'Boopac Shakur,' who outed pedophiles online, fatally shot at restaurant after accusing suspect
description: A Michigan man who used social media to attempt to catch pedophiles was fatally shot during a dispute with a person he accused of being a predator over the weekend, police say.

title: Beyoncé announces new film as U.S. leg of 'Renaissance Tour' closes
description: Get ready, Beyhive: Beyoncé just revealed that a movie based on her “Renaissance World Tour” will hit theaters in December.
